  stimulus_text = 'The popularity of the internet has made it easier than ever to learn about new things. There are thousands of websites dedicated to sharing information about any topic imaginable. And many people use the internet to research the latest news, find recipes, or learn new skills. However, the internet can also be a source of misinformation. It is important to be critical of the information you find online and to verify facts before you accept them as true.',
